replies.body:
Broporo ooooon duty! {{summoner:31}} 

Most of the time that grey play button means that your client is having a hard time getting a solid connection with our matchmaking servers. The client realizes that you might not be able to stay connected throughout the game, so it can't reliably connect you to any games.

We should be able to get that button lit back up by going through the steps in this [**connection guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues). Let me know if you have any problems along the way!
